Class PlanNodeSnapshot

  • java.lang.Object
    • iti.kukumo.api.plan.PlanNodeSnapshot
  • public class PlanNodeSnapshot
extends Object
    This class is a immutable, non-executable representation of a * PlanNode in a specific state. *

    * It is mainly used for serialization/deserialization operations. *
